0/last-week-tonight.png?fit=840%2C476&amp;ssl=1\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/vietfactcheck.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/last-week-tonight.png?resize=600%2C280&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/vietfactcheck.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/last-week-tonight.png?zoom=2&amp;resize=600%2C280&amp;ssl=1 1200w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://i0.wp.com/vietfactcheck.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/last-week-tonight.png?resize=600%2C280&amp;ssl=1&amp;is-pending-load=1\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" />\t\t\t</a>\n\n\t\t\n\t\t<header class=\"entry-header\">\n\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"https://vietfactcheck.org/2021/10/17/letter-from-the-editor-was-viet-fact-check-mentioned-on-last-week-tonight-with-john-oliver/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Letter From the Editor: Was Viet Fact Check Mentioned on “Last Week Tonight With John Oliver”?</a></h2>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"entry-meta clearfix\"><span class=\"meta-date\"><a href=\"https://vietfactcheck.org/2021/10/17/letter-from-the-editor-was-viet-fact-check-mentioned-on-last-week-tonight-with-john-oliver/\" title=\"1:48 pm\" rel=\"bookmark\"><time class=\"entry-date published updated\" datetime=\"2021-10-17T13:48:35-07:00\">October 17, 2021</time></a></span><span class=\"meta-author\"> <span class=\"author vcard\"><a class=\"url fn n\" href=\"https://vietfactcheck.org/author/diepthought/\" title=\"View all posts by diepthought\" rel=\"author\">diepthought</a></span></span></div>\n\t\t</header><!-- .entry-header -->\n\n\t\t<div class=\"entry-content entry-excerpt clearfix\">\n\n\t\t\t<p>This claim is <b>TRUE</b>! </p>\n<p>Over the summer, Viet Fact Check received an email from a producer for “Last Week Tonight with John Oliver,” a news show on HBO with 4 million viewers per episode. They wanted to devote a whole show to misinformation in non-English communities. Would we tell them about what we have noticed about this trend in the Vietnamese community? </p>\n<p>We told them what we knew. </p></div>\n<div class=\"read-more\"><a href=\"https://vietfactcheck.org/2021/10/17/letter-from-the-editor-was-viet-fact-check-mentioned-on-last-week-tonight-with-john-oliver/\" class=\"more-link\">Continue reading</a></p>\n\n\t\t</div><!-- .entry-content -->\n\n\t</article>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"post-column clearfix\">\n\n\t<article id=\"post-293\" class=\"post-293 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail sticky hentry category-chien-tranh-viet-nam category-joe-biden-vietnamese category-vietnamese tag-featured comments-off\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://vietfactcheck.org/2020/08/31/sai-su-that-biden-va-dang-dan-chu-chong-dan-ti-nan-viet-nam/\" rel=\"bookmark\">\n\t\t\t\t<img width=\"600\" height=\"280\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/vietfactcheck.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/n-VIETNAM-REFUGEE-BOAT-628x314-1.jpg?resize=600%2C280&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image jetpack-lazy-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" data-attachment-id=\"571\" data-permalink=\"https://vietfactcheck.org/2020/08/31/sai-su-that-biden-va-dang-dan-chu-chong-dan-ti-nan-viet-nam/n-vietnam-refugee-boat-628x314/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/vietfactcheck.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/n-VIETNAM-REFUGEE-BOAT-628x314-1.jpg?fit=800%2C400&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"800,400\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1368057600&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"n-VIETNAM-REFUGEE-BOAT-628&#215;314\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0